    "body": "the attestation was from some out-of-synced node which voted for some old block, lodestar used the state at that block and was not able to get committee.\r\n\r\nIn this case, since that node is out-of-synced, that attestation is not valid since validator is already not part of committee, so the error is expected. Maybe we should find a better way to log the error.",
